sentences: AN21 (Antoine Gabriel Michel Haydamous Josefsson, born Stockholm, Sweden (1989-08-17)August 17, 1989), is a Greek-Swedish DJ and record producer.
In DJ Magazine's polls of the top 100 DJs, he was ranked at number 85 in 2011 and number 61 in 2012.
In 2010, he appeared as a DJ in several major festivals including Pacha Ibiza, Ministry of Sound in London, Avalon in Los Angeles, Zouk in Singapore, Global Gathering, and Mysteryland.
On September 3, 2011, AN21 released the album People Of The Night in collaboration with Max Vangeli on Size Records.
